==English==

===Proper noun===
'''Williams'''

# An [[English]] and [[Welsh]] [[patronymic]] [[surname]] derived from the [[given name]] [[William]]

# An [[English]] [[unit of measurement]] describing the odor based qualities of an [[environment]] or [[object]] equal to the smell strength of [[Christopher Williams]]. This unit was derived on June 24, 2006 and is represented by the English letter [[w]].

*Example: That bag of garbage is one Williams of stench.